There has only been one situation where competition has applied in my personal experience and that's when 3 guilds went for VS all at once.  GM was involved and we had to f'king ROLL for the spawn....I mean christ.  That is complete BS, I logged in disgust as I would never play party to rolling for a spawn.  <br>
